Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:20.09,Style_title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs75\bord1.875\3c&HB3B4E0&\b1\shad0\c&H9DC0E6&\t(\fs52.5)\move(961.5,214.5,961.5,280.5,1,8450)}Волшебница {\fs124.5\fad(500,0)\b1\t(\fs94.5)\c&H9C94FC&\3c&HBDBDDE&\bord2.752}Мадока Магика
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:25.26,Style_opening,,0,0,0,,{\be2\blur4.5\an2}Смогу ли снова я когда-то увидать
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:27.72,Style_copyrights,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,350)\pos(1623.75,345)\blur3\be2}Перевод: junnes
